The '''''Rode to Ruin''''' was a [[Starship/Legends|ship]] owned by [[Fracca]]. It was registered on [[Orron III]] with registration number RN27-382992.

In [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] tracked this ship as it passed the inner flight control buoys of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Teyr/Legends|Teyr]].

